list.abstract: Party（英[ˈpɑːti]，美[ˈpɑːrti]），英语单词，作名词用，为社交聚会；派对；党。作动词用，为尽情欢乐；欢宴。作形容词用，为分割开的；分成不同颜色部分的。短语搭配有birthday party（生日派对），例句为“Every party needs a straight person.（每个政党都需要一个正直的人。）” Party名词类近义词有principal、get-together，复数形式为parties。
Party，是一个英语词汇，有多种意义，如：社交聚会、党派、当事人等，可根据所处的词语意境，进行不同的解释。

yingyinNormal.en: So, whose good-bye party is this anyway?
yingyinNormal.zh: 话说回来，这是谁的告别聚会？

yingyinNormal.en: Serena, that party is an important event for you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瑟琳娜，今天的聚会对你很重要。

yingyinNormal.en: You're missing the party.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么不去聚会。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, you can't say we don't know how to throw a party.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看来我们的聚会办得不错！

yingyinNormal.en: We have two days to plan this party. We just need to make fast decisions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有两天来计划这个聚会，做决定要快。

yingyinNormal.en: I can't believe we're at a real college party. I have to pee so bad.
yingyinNormal.zh: 难以置信我们在一个真的大学聚会上。我兴奋的直想尿尿。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, I hate to break up the party, but Amy says I'm tired and have to go to bed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也不想打断聚会，但艾米说我累了，必须上床睡觉。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Treeger. You said there was a party. Oh, yeah, well hey, welcome to our sauna.
yingyinNormal.zh: 崔格先生。你说有派对啊？欢迎光临我们的桑拿聚会。

yingyinNormal.en: I think I'm gonna drop by Asher's party. There's one more person I have to talk to.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想我要顺便去下阿瑟的聚会，还有一个人我必须要和她谈谈。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah? Where is it? Oh, he's playing organ for a children's roller-skating party.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在哪儿演出啊？哦，是一个少儿滚轴溜冰的聚会。他去那儿弹琴。

yingyinNormal.en: People expect you to party and be wild, sleep with whoever you want, run away, come back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家都认为你天天有聚会，生活放荡随便和人睡觉，然后离开，再回来。

yingyinNormal.en: Lady, this is my city, I'll find your friend. Alright, party is over. Miron, vacuum.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小姐，这是我的城市，我会找到你的朋友的。好了，聚会结束。迈伦，上吸尘器。

yingyinNormal.en: No, no, not a party. Just a surprise gathering of some people Rachel knows. This is Phoebe and Chandler and Joey.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，不是派对啦，只是一群瑞秋认识的人的惊喜聚会，这是菲比，钱德，乔伊。

yingyinNormal.en: Sister, you are preaching to the choir. I'm all about evolving right now. It's actually how I got into party planning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 姐们儿，你这是班门弄斧了，我无时无刻不在进化，实际上我就是这么干起聚会策划的。

yingyinNormal.en: Meaning a dumpling with Baijiu, the more you eat or drink, the richer you will be. It sounds like our sort of party, dude. It does. Baijiu, Baijiu?
yingyinNormal.zh: 就是边吃饺子边喝酒，吃喝越多就越富有。这聚会对我们胃口。是的。白酒，白酒。

yingyinNormal.en: What's wrong with you, Tarrant? You used to be the life of the party. You used to do the best Futterwacken in all of Witzend.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么啦，塔兰特？你一直都是聚会上的灵魂人物。你一直是整个维兹恩特最棒的福特沃肯舞者。

yingyinNormal.en: Why do you think that is? Because I want a party. Try again. Well, 'cause I agree with Zay. We are growing up very fast.

党指引我们从一个胜利走向另一个胜利。

全党同志在为群众的利益而奋斗。
